flowchart TD
    %% ============================================
    %% Struct Agent Team Workflow
    %% Minto 기반 구조화 에이전트 팀 전체 흐름
    %% ============================================

    subgraph User["사용자"]
        direction TB
        Call["/struct-think<br>/struct-write<br>/struct-solve<br>/struct-express<br>/struct-review"]
    end

    subgraph Skills["Skills Layer (SKILL.md)"]
        direction LR
        SThink["struct-think"]
        SWrite["struct-write<br>(template 옵션)"]
        SSolve["struct-solve"]
        SExpress["struct-express<br>(slide/memo/story)"]
        SReview["struct-review<br>(Fidelity Gate)"]
    end

    subgraph Orchestrator["Orchestrator (sonnet)"]
        direction TB
        O1["1. 커맨드 파싱<br>Task + Options 추출"]
        O2["2. .struct-memory.json 로드"]
        O3["3. 모드 감지<br>Collaborative vs Autonomous"]
        O4{"Prior Injection 필요?<br>(write / solve / express)"}
        O5["4. Prior Thinking 선택<br>유사도 + 최신 + 옵션"]
        O6["5. Prior 파일 Read +<br>## Previous Thinking Pyramid 주입"]
        O7["6. 전문 Agent 라우팅"]
    end

    subgraph Specialists["Specialist Agents"]
        direction LR
        Think["thinking.md<br>(opus)<br>Minto 6-Step"]
        Write["writing.md<br>(opus)<br>Pyramid Consumption + Template"]
        Solve["problem-solving.md<br>(opus)<br>가설 기반 문제 분석"]
        Express["expression.md<br>(sonnet)<br>슬라이드/메모/스토리 변환"]
        Review["review.md<br>(sonnet)<br>Fidelity Gate + Directives"]
    end

    subgraph Storage["Storage & Memory"]
        direction TB
        Save["struct-docs/ 저장<br>01-thinking/<br>02-writing/<br>03-solving/<br>04-expressing/<br>05-reviewing/"]
        MemUpdate[".struct-memory.json<br>previousThoughts /<br>previousDocuments 업데이트"]
    end

    %% Main Flow
    Call --> Skills
    Skills --> O1
    O1 --> O2
    O2 --> O3

    O3 --> O4
    O4 -->|Yes| O5
    O4 -->|No (think)| O7

    O5 --> O6
    O6 --> O7

    O7 --> Think
    O7 --> Write
    O7 --> Solve
    O7 --> Express
    O7 --> Review

    %% Mode 영향 (점선으로 표시)
    O3 -. Collaborative<br>중간 확인 다수 .-> Think
    O3 -. Collaborative<br>중간 확인 다수 .-> Write
    O3 -. Collaborative<br>중간 확인 다수 .-> Solve
    O3 -. Collaborative<br>중간 확인 다수 .-> Express

    O3 -. Autonomous<br>최소 요약 + 자동 .-> Think
    O3 -. Autonomous<br>최소 요약 + 자동 .-> Write
    O3 -. Autonomous<br>최소 요약 + 자동 .-> Solve
    O3 -. Autonomous<br>최소 요약 + 자동 .-> Express

    Think --> Save
    Write --> Save
    Solve --> Save
    Express --> Save

    %% Review Gate (write/solve/express 후 Orchestrator 제어)
    Write -.->|"후처리 게이트<br>(옵션)"| ReviewGate
    Solve -.->|"후처리 게이트<br>(옵션)"| ReviewGate
    Express -.->|"후처리 게이트<br>(옵션)"| ReviewGate
    ReviewGate["Review Gate<br>(Orchestrator 제어)"] --> Review
    Review --> Save

    Save --> MemUpdate
    MemUpdate --> Call

    %% Template 특수 흐름 (writing 전용)
    subgraph WritingDetail["Writing 전용"]
        direction LR
        GlobT["Glob: struct-docs/templates/*.md"]
        ReadT["선택된 템플릿 Read"]
        ApplyT["템플릿 구조 적용<br>report-default / iaej /<br>structure-event-response 등"]
    end

    Write --> GlobT
    GlobT --> ReadT
    ReadT --> ApplyT
    ApplyT --> Save

    %% Fallback (Orchestrator 실패 시)
    Fallback["직접 Specialist 호출<br>(Fallback)"]
    Skills -.->|Orchestrator 실패| Fallback
    Fallback --> Think
    Fallback --> Write
    Fallback --> Solve
    Fallback --> Express

    %% 스타일
    classDef user fill:#e3f2fd,stroke:#1976d2
    classDef skill fill:#f3e5f5,stroke:#7b1fa2
    classDef orch fill:#e8f5e9,stroke:#388e3c
    classDef spec fill:#fff3e0,stroke:#f57c00
    classDef store fill:#fce4ec,stroke:#c2185b
    classDef detail fill:#f5f5f5,stroke:#616161,stroke-dasharray: 5 5

    class Call,User user
    class SThink,SWrite,SSolve,SExpress,SReview,Skills skill
    class O1,O2,O3,O4,O5,O6,O7,Orchestrator orch
    class Think,Write,Solve,Express,Review,Specialists spec
    class Save,MemUpdate,Storage store
    class GlobT,ReadT,ApplyT,WritingDetail detail
    class ReviewGate detail
